# Tape file for the vhs tool (https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs)
# To run : vhs < version.tape
# This tape file shows the how to get the current OpenFLUID version using CLI 

Output cmdline-version.gif

Require openfluid

Set Padding 24
Set FontSize 20
Set Width 800
Set Height 320
Set LoopOffset 50%

Sleep 500ms

Type "openfluid version" Sleep 500ms  Enter

Sleep 3s
